           |               +---->|type              |   |state             | 
           |              /      |state             |   |sock              |
           v             /       |net_connection    |-->|addr              | 
   Command              /        +------------------+   |port              | 
  +-----------------+  /                                |                  |
  |                 |                                   |net_ops           |
  |                 |                                   +------------------+ 
  |                 |                                    
  |                 |                                    
